data.title: Derek Bodner
data.meta_description: Derek Bodner is a senior writer for The Athletic covering the Philadelphia 76ers. He previously reported on the team for Philadelphia Magazine and SB Nation. He has also covered the NBA Draft for USA Today and DraftExpress, and written about the NBA for The Ringer.
